fields.description:
If I stop a user-api service like compute or euare for whatever reason and that service receives a request it will still service it.  I would expect it to either reply with a redirect or a 503.

{code}
# empyrean-modify-service -t stop API_10.111.1.11.compute
# euca-describe-regions -U http://10.111.1.11:8773/services/compute
REGION	eucalyptus	http://10.111.1.11:8773/services/compute
{code}
